<article class="media box d-flex align-items-center hover-fade">
  <figure class="media-left" onclick="window.open('https://www.naver.com')">
    <p class="image clickable">
    <%= image_tag "pikapika.jpeg", class: "card-image image is-128x128" %>
    </p>
  </figure>
  <div class="media-content" onclick="window.open('https://www.naver.com')">
    <div class="content clickable">
      <p>
      <span class="title is-5">재성형은피카츄보다귀여웡뿌잉뿌잉[반값]</span><br/>
      <span class="subtitle is-6">싸게싸게더싸게옥션</span><br/>
      </p>
      <span class="tag is-success is-medium">1000원</span>
      <br/>
      <small>2017.07.03</small>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="media-right">
      <%= link_to '/mypage/toggle_like', remote: true do %>
        <div class="card-checkbox-box" data-index="<%=count%>">
          <%= image_tag 'check.png', class: "check" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
  </div>
</article>
